name: Nervous
description:
Nervous is part of the Cajal series that takes inspiration from Santiago Ramon Cajal’s illustrations of neurones. These artworks have been crafted with thoughtful insight and tender loving care. On a technical level, they mix home-brewed generative systems with hand-drawn images using Processing and GANs. 

Size : 3200x4800px PNG [bitmap image]
